snippet.title: Vyruz : Destruction of the untel empire - Intro Video
snippet.description:
I finally got my hand on the demo for this game, on an old CD. It's pretty hard to find any info on in on the internet. I can't even be sure of the year it was released : between 1997 and 2000.

I believe the name of the studio behind it is "Chiliconvalley".
